Condition.name: GET6isCMHasImpactedItemCreatable
Condition.expression: (Condition::GET6isMigrationUser(u)) OR (Condition::isActiveSequence(p) AND p.is_modifiable=true AND Condition::isRequestor(p,u) AND Condition::isAuthor(u) AND (p.CMClosure="Open" AND (p.CMDisposition="None" OR p.CMDisposition="Investigate" OR p.CMDisposition="Disapproved") AND p.CMMaturity="Elaborating") AND s.last_release_status!=NULL AND ((Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForPrimary(p,u) AND Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)))))
Condition.description: 1. Owner of Change object can only add Impacted Items. 2. Disposition, Closure and Maturity of the Change Object should have the values (Open, None and Elaborating) respectively. 3. Impacted Items should have a valid Release Status 4. IP Classification of Impacted Items should be less than or equal to the IP Classification of the Change Object

Condition.name: GET6isCMHasProblemItemCreatable
Condition.expression: (Condition::GET6isMigrationUser(u)) OR (Condition::isActiveSequence(p) AND p.is_modifiable=true AND Condition::isRequestor(p,u) AND (p.CMClosure="Open" AND (p.CMDisposition="None" OR p.CMDisposition="Investigate" OR p.CMDisposition="Disapproved") AND p.CMMaturity="Elaborating") AND s.last_release_status!=NULL AND ((Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForPrimary(p,u) AND Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)))))
Condition.description: 1. Owner of Change object can only add Problem Items. 2. Disposition, Closure and Maturity of the Change Object should have the values Open, None and Elaborating respectively. 3. Problem Items should have a valid Release Status 4. IP Classification of Problem Items should be less than or equal to the IP Classification of the Change Object

Condition.name: GET6isCMHasSolutionItemCreatable
Condition.expression: (Condition::GET6isMigrationUser(u)) OR (Condition::isActiveSequence(p) AND p.is_modifiable=true AND Condition::isRequestor(p,u) AND Condition::isAuthor(u) AND (p.CMClosure="Open" AND (p.CMDisposition="None" OR p.CMDisposition="Investigate" OR p.CMDisposition="Disapproved") AND p.CMMaturity="Elaborating") AND s.last_release_status=NULL AND ((Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForPrimary(p,u) AND Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u))) OR (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForPrimary(p,u) AND (Condition::GET6isClassificationRestrictedForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationConfidentialForSecondary(s,u) OR Condition::GET6isClassificationInternalForSecondary(s,u)))))
Condition.description: 1. Owner of Change object can only add Solution Items. 2. Disposition, Closure and Maturity of the Change Object should have the values Open, None and Elaborating respectively. 3. Solution Items should be in working status 4. IP Classification of Solution Items should be less than or equal to the IP Classification of the Change Object
